\n同埋trump個人好唔好同佢當選對香港有利係無關係的， 啲文好多鬧trump嘅野都係真同埋啱，但唔代表你唔可以策略上咁支持佢。同埋講到最尾香港人又無份投，啲文寫乜都影響唔到個結果啦，有唔同意見講幾句好正常。"},{"pid":"4a5de493db77baea971cb014064ee331af1f0e75","tid":2263474,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"557e61e606717cb0c832ad5e979b80499d9433bb","tid":2263474,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"302c5fd66e9c021b2b8bc284a89a8288003555ee","tid":2263474,"uid":224479,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f23573bf53ac210724797e87643ab84f13f8afb8","tid":2263474,"uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:59:22.000Z","msg":"知唔知咩係言論自由 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:00:49.000Z","msg":"所以689的文章都應該登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:10:29.000Z","msg":"如果佢講的野makes sense的話why not <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:27:27.000Z","msg":"how to define the boundary of making sense<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7b3a856eca3c8977dbe5aed58c508cc95d969e","tid":2263474,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96498c1585de020d63f621c3e04459c0d04b741a","tid":2263474,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a5de493db77baea971cb014064ee331af1f0e75","tid":2263474,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"557e61e606717cb0c832ad5e979b80499d9433bb","tid":2263474,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"302c5fd66e9c021b2b8bc284a89a8288003555ee","tid":2263474,"uid":224479,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:00:49.000Z","msg":"所以689的文章都應該登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\"